sequenceDiagram
    participant CI as CI/CD Pipeline<br/>(Konflux/Tekton)
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>Go CLI
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant Container as Data Container<br/>odh-model-metadata-collection
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard

    Note over CI,FS: Flow 1: Model Catalog Generation (Build Time)
    CI->>Extractor: Execute model-extractor CLI
    Extractor->>FS: Read data/models-index.yaml
    FS-->>Extractor: Model index entries

    Extractor->>HF: GET /api/users/RedHatAI/collections<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN (optional)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    HF-->>Extractor: Collection list with model IDs

    loop For each model (max 5 concurrent)
        Extractor->>OCI: GET manifest + layers<br/>TLS 1.2+, public pull
        OCI-->>Extractor: Modelcar image layers + config blobs
        Extractor->>Extractor: Parse modelcard YAML frontmatter
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{model_id}<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN (optional)
        HF-->>Extractor: Model details, README, tags
        Extractor->>Extractor: Multi-source metadata fusion<br/>(HF YAML > HF API > HF tags > modelcard)
        Extractor->>FS: Write output/{model}/metadata.yaml<br/>+ enrichment.yaml
    end

    Extractor->>FS: Write data/models-catalog.yaml
    Extractor->>FS: Read input/mcp_servers/*.yaml

    Note over Extractor,OCI: Flow 2: MCP Server Catalog Generation (Build Time)
    loop For each MCP server
        Extractor->>OCI: GET manifest for MCP image<br/>TLS 1.2+, public pull
        OCI-->>Extractor: Architecture list + timestamps
        Extractor->>Extractor: Enrich MCP server metadata
    end

    Extractor->>FS: Write data/redhat-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml

    Note over CI,Container: Flow 3: Container Image Build
    CI->>CI: Dockerfile.konflux: COPY data/*.yaml /app/data/
    CI->>Container: Build + publish multi-arch image<br/>(x86_64, ppc64le, s390x, arm64)

    Note over Container,Dashboard: Flow 4: Runtime Catalog Consumption
    Container->>Container: Entrypoint: sleep infinity
    Dashboard->>Container: Mount /app/data/ volume
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Read models-catalog.yaml<br/>+ mcp-servers-catalog.yaml<br/>Display in UI
